---
title: David Burtka’s Zesty Shrimp & Slaw Tacos with Creamy Guac, Salsa & Blue Corn Chips
description: Professional chef David knows a terrific taco comes down to the details: slaw tossed with pickled onion and cilantro, creamy guacamole with a hint of lime zest, and succulent shrimp seasoned with a curated blend of Mexican spices. These tacos also star a side of chunky salsa with tomato, corn, black beans, bell pepper, and jalapeño—perfect for dipping with blue corn tortilla chips. His husband Neil Patrick Harris gives this dish five stars, which can only mean one thing: When it comes to tacos, David knows best!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/david-burtkas-zesty-shrimp-slaw-tacos-9e3ed9de.jpg
